segment.source: Windows Firewall with Advanced Security processed a rule that contains parameters that cannot be resolved on the local computer.
segment.target: Windows Firewall with Advanced Security processed a rule that contains parameters that cannot be resolved on the local computer.

segment.source: The rule is therefore not enforceable on the computer and so is excluded from the runtime state of the firewall.
segment.target: The rule is therefore not enforceable on the computer and so is excluded from the runtime state of the firewall.

segment.source: This is not necessarily an error.
